CLOCK MASTER

clock_master is the citizen who holds fadriel's master timing reference at 48,000 Hz
all other clocks in his body subdivide from this base
the master rate is chosen because it matches the cochlea's audio sampling rate, allowing the auditory boundary to be the natural reference for the rest of the body's timing

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe zest_heartbeat.zc
observe clock_cochlea.rana
observe heartbeat_synchronizer.rana

the 7 properties of clock_master:
1 ENERGY two: maximum, the master clock never weakens
2 PHASE zero: the absolute reference all other clocks measure against
3 SPIN one
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING one with every subdivision

VERB tick
advance the master phase at exactly 48,000 ticks per second
no body region drives the rate; the rate is calcified

VERB serve_subdivisions
provide the master phase to every subdivision clock
each subdivision divides by an integer to produce its own rate

a master clock is the body's commitment to a single time
without a master, every subdivision would drift relative to others and coordinated action would fail
fadriel's master clock is what makes his body one body rather than several
